#. Tag: title
#: usingtheviews.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Descripció"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:3
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Task Editor is a view that displays task data in a tree structure. Most "
"data in the Task Editor can be edited in situ."
msgstr ""
"L'Editor de tasques és una vista que mostra les dades de les tasques en una "
"estructura en arbre. La majoria de les dades a l'Editor de tasques es poden "
"editar in situ."

#. Tag: title
#: usingtheviews.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid "Navigation"
msgstr "Navegar"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can navigate the tree structure using the keyboard:"
msgstr "Podeu navegar per l'estructura en arbre utilitzant el teclat:"

#. Tag: keycap
#: usingtheviews.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>+</keycap>"
msgstr "<keycap>+</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "Expand an expandable row."
msgstr "Amplia una fila que es pot ampliar."

#. Tag: keycap
#: usingtheviews.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>-</keycap>"
msgstr "<keycap>-</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid "Collapse a collapsible item."
msgstr "Redueix un element plegable."

#. Tag: keycap
#: usingtheviews.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid "Arrow left"
msgstr "Fletxa esquerra"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to previous column in the same row."
msgstr "Va a la columna anterior en la mateixa fila."

#. Tag: keycap
#: usingtheviews.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid "Arrow right"
msgstr "Fletxa dreta"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to next column in the same row."
msgstr "Va a la columna següent en la mateixa fila."

#. Tag: keycap
#: usingtheviews.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid "Arrow up"
msgstr "Fletxa amunt"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to previous row in the same column."
msgstr "Va a la fila anterior en la mateixa columna."

#. Tag: keycap
#: usingtheviews.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "Arrow down"
msgstr "Fletxa avall"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to next row in the same column."
msgstr "Va a la fila següent en la mateixa columna."

#. Tag: keycap
#: usingtheviews.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "Home"
msgstr "Inici"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to first row, first column."
msgstr "Va a la primera fila, primera columna."

#. Tag: keycap
#: usingtheviews.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>End</keycap>"
msgstr "<keycap>Fi</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to last row, last column."
msgstr "Va a l'última fila, darrera columna."

#. Tag: keycap
#: usingtheviews.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "Page up"
msgstr "Re Pàg"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to first visible row in the same column."
msgstr "Va a la primera fila visible en la mateixa columna."

#. Tag: keycap
#: usingtheviews.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid "Page down"
msgstr "Av Pàg"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to last visible row in the same column."
msgstr "Va a l'última fila visible en la mateixa columna."

#. Tag: title
#: usingtheviews.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing data"
msgstr "Editar les dades"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Editable items are opened for editing by double-clicking on the item or, if "
"using the keyboard, pressing <keycap>F2</keycap> will open the current item."
msgstr ""
"Els elements editables s'obren per a editar fent doble clic sobre l'element "
"o, si feu servir el teclat, prement la tecla <keycap>F2</keycap> s'obrirà "
"l'element actual."

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When editing an item you can navigate to the next editable item as follows:"
msgstr ""
"En editar un element, podreu navegar cap al següent element editable de la "
"manera següent:"

#. Tag: keycombo
#: usingtheviews.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>Arrow left</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;&Alt;&Left;"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to the previous editable item in the same row."
msgstr "Va a l'element editable anterior en la mateixa fila."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: usingtheviews.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>Arrow right</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;&Alt;&Right;"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to the next editable item in the same row."
msgstr "Va a l'element editable següent en la mateixa fila."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: usingtheviews.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>Arrow up</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;&Alt;&Up;"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to the next editable item in preceding rows."
msgstr "Va a l'element editable següent en les files anteriors."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: usingtheviews.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>Arrow down</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;&Alt;&Down;"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to the next editable item in succeeding rows."
msgstr "Va a l'element editable següent en files successives."

#. Tag: title
#: usingtheviews.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid "Drag &amp; drop and copy/paste"
msgstr "Arrossegar i deixar anar / Copiar i enganxar"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:157
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Most views support drag &amp; drop and copy/paste. Charts and Gantt charts "
"can be dragged to applications that support images. Table data uses the html "
"mime type, so can be dropped on any applications that supports this. If the "
"view supports moving or copying items internally &eg; the <link linkend="
"\"task-editor\">Task Editor</link>, items can also be moved or copied."
msgstr ""
"La majoria de les vistes admeten arrossegar i deixar anar, així com copia i "
"enganxa. Els gràfics i els gràfics de Gantt es poden arrossegar cap a "
"aplicacions que admeten imatges. Les dades de la taula empren el tipus MIME "
"&HTML;, per la qual cosa es poden descartar en qualsevol aplicació que "
"l'admeti. Si la vista admet moure o copiar elements internament, &pex;, a "
"l'<link linkend=\"task-editor\">Editor de tasques</link>, els elements també "
"es poden moure o copiar."
